cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on spectrum management and network resource management, which are key topics in networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - Spectrum sensing is also important for security purposes, such as detecting unauthorized transmissions or interference. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses techniques for efficient spectrum management, which can be related to information theory and communication theory. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The proposed system for detecting and consuming spectrum events can be seen as a control system for managing wireless resources. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper mentions the ability to enable application development through custom querying of detected events, which can involve machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques.
